net.sf.marineapi.nmea.sentence

Interface VBWSentence

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Sentence

    public interface VBWSentence
extends Sentence

    VBW Dual Ground/Water Speed Longitudinal, Transverse and Stern Ground/Water Speed with Status.

    Example:
    $IIVBW,11.0,02.0,A,06.0,03.0,A,05.3,A,01.0,A*43

    Author:
    Jeremy Wilson
